RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: Select DISTINCT (a.agency_ref_no),c.cusip_no,c.currency,c.branch From tltb_dcf_amount_due a, oltbs_contract b, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER c WHERE a.agency_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no and c.contract_ref_no = a.agency_ref_no and c.version_no=(SELECT max (version_no) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER WHERE contract_ref_no=a.agency_ref_no) and b.branch = global.current_branch AND nvl(a.amount_due, 0) > 0

select distinct(a.counterparty) from tltb_contract_master a,oltbs_contract b where a.cusip_no=? AND a.quotation ='F' AND a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND a.version_no = b.latest_version_no AND b.contract_status='L' AND EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM tltb_dcf_amount_due c WHERE c.trade_ref_no=a.contract_ref_no AND c.counterparty= a.counterparty)

SELECT SSI_MNEMONIC,CURRENCY,COUNTERPARTY,SETTLEMENT_SEQ_NO,MODULE,PRODUCT_CODE,BRANCH FROM OLTM_INSTR A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE A.BRANCH ='ALL' AND A.MODULE='AL' AND A.COUNTERPARTY=? AND A.CURRENCY = '*.*' AND A.PRODUCT_CODE ='ALL' AND A.AUTH_STAT ='A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.CUSTOMER_NO=A.COUNTERPARTY ORDER BY 3,2

select b.entity, b.entity_name, b.entity_type, b.PHONE_NO, b.FAX_NO, b.EMAIL from OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY a, OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS b where a.customer_no = ? and a.record_stat = 'O' and a.auth_stat = 'A' and b.customer_no = a.customer_no Order by b.entity
